com.opensymphony.xwork2.interceptor

Interface WithLazyParams


  • public interface WithLazyParams
    Interceptors marked with this interface won't be fully initialised during initialisation. Appropriated params will be injected just before usage of the interceptor. Please be aware that in such case Interceptor.init() method must be prepared for this.
    Since:
    2.5.9
